org.eclipse.gef4.dot.internal

Class DotLanguageSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.gef4.dot.internal.DotLanguageSupport

  • public class DotLanguageSupport
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides access to parsers, serializers, and validators of the respective Dot language grammars.

      • parseAttributeValue

        public static <T> T parseAttributeValue(DotLanguageSupport.IPrimitiveValueParser<T> parser,
                                        java.lang.String attributeValue)
        Parses the given (unquoted) attribute, using the given DotLanguageSupport.IPrimitiveValueParser.
        Type Parameters:
        T - The (primitive) object type of the parsed value.
        Parameters:
        parser - The parser to be used for parsing.
        attributeValue - The (unquoted) attribute value that is to be parsed.
        Returns:
        The parsed value, or null if the value could not be parsed.
